replies.body:
Same here.  I just played a game where my ult went through people and did no damage 4 times during the game (unfortunately getting me killed as it happened because it left me wide open).  We won anyways thankfully, but riot c'mon... all your fixes keep coming back with more bugs.

I also main Azir, I like the champion a lot.  It seems to me though he worked better on release than he does right now.  So what if his ult sometimes double bounced people or could pin to a wall?  That's what was supposed to make his ult good.  Now it effectively does nothing.  So it's like your r is blank. :/

Please fix,  from an Azir main.{{champion:268}}
